{
  "id": "69aee010cab8370a3d540b47",
  "title": "音素ベクトルに分解する",
  "created": 1773068306,
  "updated": 1778197844,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69aee010cab8370a3d540b47",
      "text": "音素ベクトルに分解する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068306,
      "updated": 1773068306
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee0120000000000579371",
      "text": "#怪文書の書き方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068306,
      "updated": 1773068313
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee0190000000000579373",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068314,
      "updated": 1773068314
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee0190000000000579374",
      "text": "[日本語の文字種数を下げる]が思いの外規則的になったので音素ベクトルのようなものを作ると面白そう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068314,
      "updated": 1773068368
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee0500000000000579377",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068369,
      "updated": 1773068369
    },
    {
      "id": "69afa0d40000000000cd1b5a",
      "text": "要素",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773117654,
      "updated": 1773117658
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee07b00000000005793a8",
      "text": " 有声音「+」無声音「-」（鼻音「n」正門摩擦音「h」弾き音「r」母音「 」）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068412,
      "updated": 1773117665
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee08000000000005793aa",
      "text": " 唇音「p」歯音「t」口蓋音「k」（弾き音「r」母音「 」）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068417,
      "updated": 1773117666
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee08000000000005793ab",
      "text": " 破裂音「d」摩擦音「s」鼻音「n」弾き音「r」（母音「 」）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068417,
      "updated": 1773117667
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee08100000000005793ac",
      "text": " 硬口蓋接近音挿入「j」 ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068417,
      "updated": 1773117668
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee08100000000005793ad",
      "text": " 前舌母音「i」中舌母音「a」後舌母音「u」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068418,
      "updated": 1773117669
    },
    {
      "id": "69af933c0000000000c021d9",
      "text": " 広母音「a」中母音「o」狭母音「-」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773114173,
      "updated": 1773117670
    },
    {
      "id": "69af93400000000000c021da",
      "text": " 促音「っ」撥音「ん」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773114177,
      "updated": 1773117671
    },
    {
      "id": "69af940e0000000000c021db",
      "text": "単語の間を分かち書き",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773114383,
      "updated": 1773114398
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee07c00000000005793a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773068413,
      "updated": 1773068413
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd25470000000000d58d88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778197832,
      "updated": 1778197832
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd253f0000000000d58d87",
      "text": "結果",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778197823,
      "updated": 1778197832
    },
    {
      "id": "69fd25530000000000d58d89",
      "text": "自由研究的なであり、個人のプロジェクトに帰属すべきだと思ったので切り出し。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778197844,
      "updated": 1778197844
    },
    {
      "id": "69aee0500000000000579378",
      "text": "✂ [/Summer498/音素ベクトルに分解する#69fd2490000000000084f2ab]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
